main event: A witness observed multiple unidentified flying objects over Redding, California on May 7, 1952.
interesting points: The witness saw 7 or 8 objects traveling in a straight line at a very fast speed with no sound.
The objects were observed for approximately 15 minutes.
The objects were seen at a very high altitude over the Redding, California airport.
The witness described the objects as having a whitish or silvery color and making a very faint circular motion.
The witness was unable to determine what the objects were, but stated they did not resemble any known aircraft.
